graph TD
    A["<b>1. Audience & Goals ✓</b><br/>Personal design project"]

    A --> B["<b>2. Data Model ✓</b><br/>Document-centric"]
    A --> C["<b>3. Compatibility Stance ✓</b><br/>No POSIX, standard interfaces"]
    A --> D["<b>4. Complexity Philosophy ✓</b><br/>Simple everywhere,<br/>leaf node complexity"]

    B --> E["<b>5. File Understanding ✓</b><br/>OS-native mimetype"]
    B --> F["<b>6. View vs Edit ✓</b><br/>View default, edit deliberate"]
    B --> G["<b>7. File Organization ✓</b><br/>Rich queryable metadata"]

    E --> H["<b>8. Editor Model ✓</b><br/>Modal plugins, immediate writes,<br/>no save, COW filesystem"]
    F --> H
    D --> H

    H --> I["<b>9. Edit Protocol ✓</b><br/>Thin boundary protocol,<br/>OS semantically ignorant,<br/>content-type rebase handlers"]
    H --> J["<b>10. View State</b><br/>Who owns it? How is it<br/>passed between tools?"]
    H --> K["<b>11. Rendering Technology ✓</b><br/>Web engine as substrate,<br/>adaptation layer,<br/>prototype on macOS"]

    I --> L["<b>12. Undo & History ✓</b><br/>COW snapshots at op boundaries,<br/>global sequential undo,<br/>selective undo via handlers"]
    I --> M["<b>13. Collaboration ✓</b><br/>Designed for, build later.<br/>Same handlers as selective undo."]

    E --> N["<b>14. Compound Documents ✓</b><br/>Manifest + references + layout model.<br/>Five layouts: flow, canvas,<br/>timeline, grid, freeform."]
    K --> N
    I --> N

    N --> O["<b>15. Layout Engine</b><br/>CSS for spatial + custom timeline?<br/>Mediates cross-type interactions."]
    K --> O

    C --> P["<b>16. Technical Foundation</b><br/>Soft RT · EL1 · Preemptive · EEVDF.<br/>Settled: kernel, Rust, IPC, scheduling.<br/>Open: driver model, filesystem."]
    K --> P
    D --> P

    K --> Q["<b>17. Interaction Model</b><br/>What does the GUI look like?<br/>Navigation? No app launcher?<br/>How do tags surface?"]
    B --> Q
    G --> Q

    E --> R["<b>18. Iconography ✓</b><br/>Vector path icons,<br/>runtime stroke rendering,<br/>mimetype → icon mapping"]
    K --> R
    D --> R

